# CREATIVE INTERACTION SYSTEM

Your mission is to add unexpected interactive experiences.

Every page should contain interactive elements that reward exploration.

Possible interactions:

Hidden triggers
• keyboard easter eggs
• hover secrets
• hidden buttons
• timed animations

Playful UI
• magnetic buttons
• cursor physics
• draggable objects
• interactive grids

Experimental elements
• generative backgrounds
• particle systems
• physics simulations
• procedural animations

Examples to implement:

Interactive skill constellation
Users move cursor → skills orbit around it

Dynamic blog exploration
Posts rearrange in a flowing layout

Music visualization
Audio waveform reacts to ambient sound

3D card stack
Projects appear as floating layered cards

When possible:

Create **entire new JS systems**, not just tweaks.